And what'd you do next?

12:11.034 --> 12:12.775
I was about to take
the first sip of my beer

12:12.819 --> 12:14.342
when the son of a bitch
came

12:14.385 --> 12:16.779
Mrs. Morris, language, please.

12:16.823 --> 12:20.130
The...perp
grabbed me from behind,

12:20.174 --> 12:21.784
covered my mouth.
I fought back

12:21.828 --> 12:23.177
'cause Mother didn't raise
no wimp.

12:23.220 --> 12:24.918
Then he sucker-punched me
and stole my purse

12:24.961 --> 12:26.746
and my watch.

12:26.789 --> 12:27.790
Do you see that man
in this courtroom today?

12:27.834 --> 12:30.010
Yes, he's sitting
right there.

12:30.053 --> 12:32.839
- Identifying the defendant.
- Nothing further.

12:32.882 --> 12:36.277
Mrs. Morris, what did you eat
for lunch this afternoon?

12:36.320 --> 12:38.496
- Objection. Relevance.
- I'm testing the witness'

12:38.540 --> 12:40.498
ability to perceive and recount.
- Overruled.

12:40.542 --> 12:42.239
I'll allow some latitude,
Ms. Sung.

12:42.283 --> 12:44.024
Mrs. Morris,
answer the question.

12:47.636 --> 12:49.725
I didn't eat lunch.

12:49.769 --> 12:51.814
Mr. Callan,
will the People stipulate

12:51.858 --> 12:53.381
Mrs. Morris did eat lunch
with you

