12:58.647 --> 13:01.781
Yes. The People stipulate
that Mrs. Morris

13:01.824 --> 13:03.217
did eat lunch today.

13:03.260 --> 13:05.219
You can all kiss my ass!

13:05.262 --> 13:07.395
- Mrs. Morris!
- How would you like it if you

13:07.438 --> 13:09.527
were poked and prodded
